channel.title: My custom Xen map has very low FPS
channel.description: Well,it isn't fully my map. I'm actually trying to update HECU_MARINE's Xen map and also fix some bugs. The framerate is unplayable and I always get error code 1 on VVIS. I have an Intel Core i7-6700 CPU and a Nvidia Geforce GTX 1060 GPU. It's also probably my fault. Help please!

item.title: My custom Xen map has very low FPS
item.dc:creator: Admiral_Sakai
item.description:
In the “Map” menu, click “Load Portalfile” and see if anything comes up. If you get a file window, close that and try “load pointfile”. This will show you if you have any leaks or other optimization anomalies in the map.
